Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.80,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Anou... Mitaka-senpai?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.17,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Ya, Aoyama-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.17,0:07:51.91,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Cái này có phải là thư tình không?
